---
import Layout from './layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Why Health Testing Matters in Dog Breeding"
  description="Learn about the importance of health testing in responsible dog breeding practices."
>
  <!-- Blog Post Content -->
  <section class="bg-body py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row gy-4">
        <div class="col-lg-9 order-lg-2">
          <!-- Blog Heading, Category, and Date -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="badge text-primary bg-primary-subtle fs-6 mb-2">Health</span>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-2">Why Health Testing Matters in Dog Breeding</h1>
            <p class="text-muted"><i class="ri-calendar-line me-1"></i>12 Jan 2025</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Cover Image -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <img
              src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/golden-retriever-1.jpg"
              alt="Blog Cover"
              class="img-fluid rounded-5"
              style="max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%;"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Blog Content -->
          <div class="fs-5 mb-4">
            <p>
              Breeding dogs responsibly requires more than just a passion for the breed — it demands
              a commitment to health and genetic screening. Health testing plays a pivotal role in
              reducing inherited diseases and ensuring the well-being of future litters.
            </p>
            <p>
              Through responsible breeding practices, including thorough health evaluations,
              breeders contribute to the long-term health of dog populations. Tests such as hip
              evaluations, genetic screenings, and cardiac exams help breeders make informed pairing
              decisions.
            </p>
            <p>
              Investing in health testing also builds trust with prospective puppy buyers,
              reinforces ethical breeding standards, and ultimately leads to healthier, happier
              pets.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Share Button -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <button class="btn btn-lg btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4">
              <i class="ri-share-line me-1"></i> Share this post
            </button>
          </div>

          <!-- Author Section -->
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center border-top pt-4 mb-5">
            <img
              src="/dist/assets/img/avatars/avatar1.jpg"
              alt="Author Image"
              class="rounded-circle me-3"
              width="64"
              height="64"
            />
            <div>
              <h5 class="mb-1">
                <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none text-body">Jane Smith</a>
              </h5>

              <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                Certified canine health advocate with 10+ years of experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Similar Posts -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h4 class="mb-4">Similar Posts</h4>
            <div class="row g-4">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border rounded-5 h-100 p-0">
                  <img
                    src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/golden-retriever-1.jpg"
                    class="card-img-top rounded-top-5"
                    alt="Similar Post 1"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <h5 class="card-title">
                      Puppy Mills vs. Ethical Breeders: Learn the Difference
                    </h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted mb-2">
                      Comparing unethical breeding operations to responsible ones, with clear
                      distinctions.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-link text-primary p-0">Read more</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border rounded-5 h-100 p-0">
                  <img
                    src="/dist/assets/img/breederspot-images/golden-retriever-1.jpg"
                    class="card-img-top rounded-top-5"
                    alt="Similar Post 2"
                  />
                  <div class="card-body p-3">
                    <h5 class="card-title">The True Cost of a Well-Bred Puppy</h5>
                    <p class="card-text text-muted mb-2">
                      Why puppies from ethical breeders cost more and what goes into responsible
                      pricing.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-link text-primary p-0">Read more</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Sidebar Column -->
        <div class="col-lg-3 order-lg-1">
          <div class="sticky-top z-1" style="top: 80px;">
            <!-- Popular Posts Card -->
            <div class="card border rounded-5 p-3 mb-4">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title mb-3">
                  <i class="ri-history-line me-2"></i>Popular Posts
                </h5>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                  <li class="list-group-item">
                    <a href="#" class="text-decoration-none fw-semibold d-block mb-1">
